Symless hereby grants you a non-transferable, non-exclusive licence to use the Synergy software on your devices in accordance with the terms of this EULA agreement.

You are permitted to load the Synergy software (for example a PC, laptop, mobile or tablet) under your control. You are responsible for ensuring your device meets the minimum requirements of the Synergy software.

With exception to open-source components, you are not permitted to:

    Edit, alter, modify, adapt, translate or otherwise change the whole or any part of the Software nor permit the whole or any part of the Software to be combined with or become incorporated in any other software, nor decompile, disassemble or reverse engineer the Software or attempt to do any such things
